text:
I have been trying to install kb890830 in Windows Server 2019 and no success.
the installation completes without giving any error. 
I tried the following scripts. 
Start-Process -FilePath
"C:\tmp\windows-kb890830-x64-v5.118_1898d7783231ed14970911d2c4dd815be13e2a4a.exe"
-ArgumentList "/q" -Wait 
Start-Process -FilePath
"C:\tmp\windows-kb890830-x64-v5.118_1898d7783231ed14970911d2c4dd815be13e2a4a.exe"
-Wait 
I can install all other windows updates. It is fully updated. 
I have read similar questions regarding this problem, but they did not provide
an answer.
Does anyone have any suggestions? 
--
%40googlegroups.com
